<h2>3 · Show Your Work 📸🎥</h2>
<p>Load the world. Stand on your home spot. Type <code>SPIRAL</code> in the chat and watch the loop build all 7 walls. Walk around the pattern — see the tiny 1-block step out front and the tall 7-high wall at the back.</p>
